# Markdown Output Example

## Query 

From in progess (udr-pak)[https://github.com/TristanJamesBall/udr-pak]

```sql
select
    prng()            as prng,
    uuidv7()          as uuidv7,
    realtime_dt()     as realtime,
    clocktick_s()     as clocktick_s,
    sysdate           as sysdate,
    s1                as seq_plus,
    s2                as seq_minus,
    s3                as seq10
from
    table( seq(1,1,2) ) as seq1(s1)
cross join
    table( seq(-2) ) as seq2(s2)
cross join
    table( seq(0,10,30) ) as seq3(s3);
```

## Command

```
sqlcmd -F markdown -d tjb sql/demo_small.sql >>../ifx-sqlcmd/markdown_out.md
```
